@startuml
!theme plain
hide footbox
autonumber

actor "APP" as APP
participant "Middleware" as MW
participant "Banco de Comercio" as BDC

title GET /bdc/auth/status
APP -> MW: GET /bdc/auth/status
MW -> MW: Validar Authorization Bearer (JWT APP)
MW -> MW: Leer estado cache token BDC
note over BDC
Sin llamada externa al banco
end note
MW --> APP: 200 estado autenticación

@enduml
